程序包 achieve

类 std_Achieve

java.lang.Object
achieve.achieve
achieve.std_Achieve
public class std_Achieve extends achieve
The std_Achieve class extends the achieve class and provides methods to manage achievements for users. Achievements are stored in a map where the username is the key and the list of achievements is the value.

  • 方法详细资料

    • addAchievement

      public void addAchievement(String username, String achievement)
      Adds an achievement for the specified username. If the username already has achievements, the new achievement is added to the existing list. If the username does not exist, a new list is created for the user's achievements.
      覆盖:
      addAchievement 在类中 achieve
      参数:
      username - the username of the user
      achievement - the achievement to be added

    • removeAchievement

      public void removeAchievement(String username, String achievement)
      Removes an achievement for the specified username. If the user exists, the specified achievement is removed from their list of achievements.
      覆盖:
      removeAchievement 在类中 achieve
      参数:
      username - the username of the user
      achievement - the achievement to be removed

    • modifyAchievement

      public void modifyAchievement(String username, String oldAchievement, String newAchievement)
      Modifies an existing achievement for the specified username. If the username has any achievements, the old achievement is replaced with the new achievement.
      覆盖:
      modifyAchievement 在类中 achieve
      参数:
      username - the username of the user
      oldAchievement - the old achievement to be modified
      newAchievement - the new achievement to replace the old achievement

    • getAchievements

      public List<String> getAchievements(String username)
      Retrieves the list of achievements for the specified username. If the username has no achievements, an empty list is returned.
      参数:
      username - the username of the user
      返回:
      the list of achievements for the user
